caseTitle: Application by Muhammad Younis against Arif Mehmood Gill, MPA
authorJudge: MR. JUSTICE TASSADUQ HUSSAIN JILLANI, HCJ
tagline: No conclusive finding with regard to the authenticity of the FA degree of the respondent can be given in these proceedings and the applicant may take recourse to other remedy, if available under the law. The suo moto notice issued to the respondent as also the order of suspension of his membership from the Provincial Assembly is withdrawn.
